A horrible trick on a petrol attendant has prompted acts of kindness from social media users. They've been donating to Wiseman Ndabezitha, who was tricked by a customer. Courtesy #DStv403 DURBAN - Petrol attendant Wiseman Ndabezitha has revealed how he plans on using the money he has received from generous South Africans. A horrible trick on him prompted acts of kindness from social media users. A viral video shows the attendant being only paid a fraction of the petrol he pumped into a vehicle. WATCH: When serving a jerk pays off It prompted the hashtag #210ForWiseman. Ndabezitha says he plans on building his mother a house, renovating his own home, obtaining a license, buying a vehicle or alternatively start farming. He says the incident has deeply hurt.